name: Frupu VR Fruit Punch
summary: Get ready to dive into the ultimate action-packed VR adventure with Frupu VR Fruit Punch! Battle against the monstrous Mu and his army of fruits, as you mix and match to create delicious fruit cocktails that pack a punch. But be warned, these fruits are not your average ones. They're explosive and ready to knock you off your game. It's up to you to stay on your toes and use your lightning-fast reflexes to dodge and strike back.
